0once%20I%20returned%2C%20would%20make%20me%20more%20susceptible%20to%20a%20layoff.%20Two%20weeks%20before%20my%20delivery%2C%20Google%20announced%20its%20biggest%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-jobs-alphabet-work-employees-staff-sundar-pichai-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E12%2C000-people%20layoff%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20someone%20on%20an%20H1-B%20visa%2C%20a%20layoff%20would%20mean%20I%20would%20have%20to%20find%20another%20job%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%20or%20risk%20having%20to%20move%20back%20to%20India%20with%20a%20newborn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20came%20back%20to%20work%2C%20I%20was%20not%20a%20hundred%20percent%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20not%20as%20a%20person%20and%20not%20as%20an%20employee.%20I%20was%20not%20a%20hundred%20percent%20efficient.%20I've%20had%20my%20moments%20where%20I%20broke%20down%20and%20lost%20my%20train%20of%20thought%20during%20a%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20my%20efforts%2C%20some%20other%20senior%20people%20were%20preferred%20by%20the%20business%20partners%20for%20some%20responsibilities.%20To%20add%20to%20it%2C%20Google%20was%20entering%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20industry.%20Being%20away%20months%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Efelt%20like%20I%20was%20behind%20by%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20able%20to%20turn%20my%20performance%20around.%20In%202024%2C%20I%20got%20awards%20for%20my%20performance%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20the%20opposite%20of%20how%20last%20year%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20four%20things%20I%20did%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20easier%20on%20myself%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221965c765-0d18-468d-848b-ba5321b7d469%5C%22%3E1.%20Split%20up%20my%20leave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20offers%20employees%20the%20flexibility%20to%20take%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-denmark-one-year-paid-parental-leave-cut-short-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emater