ike%20in%20American%20boxing%2C%20which%20allows%20spectators%20to%20root%20for%20an%20underdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20match%2C%20my%20husband%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20try.%20He%20cautiously%20stepped%20into%20the%20ring%20with%20the%20largest%20of%20the%20two%20wrestlers%20and%20went%20through%20the%20entire%20ritual%20%E2%80%94%20tossing%20the%20rice%20in%20the%20air%2C%20bowing%2C%20clapping%2C%20crouching%20down%20with%20his%20fists%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20mirroring%20the%20correct%20footwork%2C%20and%20facing%20his%20opponent.%20I%20went%20next.%20Then%20each%20of%20my%20boys%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20test%20their%20mettle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20referee%20%E2%80%94%20dressed%20in%20a%20long%20red%20and%20gold%20robe%2C%20black%20pointed%20hat%2C%20white%20belt%2C%20and%20holding%20a%20small%20paper%20fan%20%E2%80%94%20officiated%2C%20my%20boys%20followed%20the%20ceremonial%20tasks%20and%20squared%20off%20with%20their%20skilled%20challenger.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20how%20the%20athlete%2C%20who%20seemed%20so%20imposing%20when%20he%20was%20brawling%20with%20his%20opponent%2C%20morphed%20into%20a%20playful%20fellow%20when%20my%20kids%20each%20entered%20the%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222415%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumo%20wrestler%20holding%20kid%20at%20Kehayaza%20Sumo%20Museum%20in%20Katsuragi%20City%2C%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6780cd8688b000981b4a505d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221898%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20youngest%20son%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20sumo%20wrestler.%3Cp%3EWendy%20Altschuler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20near-naked%20wrestler%20picked%20up%20my%20firstborn%20son%2C%20who%20was%2012%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20swung%20him%20around%20by%20his%20mawashi%2C%20I%20roared%20with%20laughter.%20I%20still%20smile%20when%20I%20think%20about%20how%20high-pitched%20the%20wrestler's%20gig