likes-this-version-of-viral-lip-reading-where-obama-calls-kamala-harris-horrendous%2Famp_articleshow%2F117179288.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20save%20your%20TikTok%20videos%20before%20the%20US%20bans%20the%20app%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20are%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20save%20your%20TikTok%20content%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6782c35650dfd88e193dff84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20are%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20save%20your%20TikTok%20content%20with%20a%20possible%20ban%20in%20the%20United%20States%20approaching.%3Cp%3EJaap%20Arriens%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETikTok%20faces%20a%20potential%20US%20ban%20if%20its%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20doesn't%20find%20a%20buyer%20in%20about%20a%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETikTok%20allows%20users%20to%20download%20and%20save%20video%20content%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20tedious.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20competitors%2C%20like%20Triller%2C%20also%20offer%20ways%20to%20migrate%20TikTok%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20potential%20TikTok%20ban%20in%20the%20United%20States%20fast%20approaching%2C%20some%20social%20media%20users%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20way%20to%20archive%20their%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20passed%20a%20law%20last%20year%20that%20would%20limit%20the%20influence%20of%20social%20media%20apps%20tied%20to%20countries%20the%20United%20States%20deems%20foreign%20adversaries.%20The%20US%20then%20gave%20TikTok's%20parent%20company%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20which%20is%20Chinese%2C%20a%20January%2019%20deadline%20to%20find%20a%20buyer%20for%20the%20app%20in%20the%20United%20States%20or%20face%20a%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20then%20challenged%20the%20law%20in%20court.%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20heard%20arguments%20from%20TikTok%20and%20the%20Biden%