20to%20videos%2C%20profile%20information%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETriller%20sends%20users%20an%20email%20once%20all%20of%20their%20TikTok%20content%20has%20been%20downloaded.%20Then%2C%20users%20have%20to%20make%20a%20Triller%20account%20and%20follow%20instructions%20on%20uploading%20their%20TikTok%20content%20onto%20the%20Triller%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22373e6f77-8de9-4d70-84a0-c228ceb9cd36%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20save%20your%20TikTok%20videos%20manually%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20users%20who%20want%20to%20avoid%20giving%20their%20personal%20information%20to%20yet%20another%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20save%20their%20TikTok%20content%20is%20likely%20already%20inside%20the%20app.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20is%20a%20more%20tedious%20process%2C%20TikTok%20allows%20users%20to%20download%20their%20content%20one%20video%20at%20a%20time%20from%20inside%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20TikTok%20app%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20any%20video%20you%20want%20to%20download%2C%20press%20the%20%26quot%3BShare%26quot%3B%20button%2C%20and%20tap%20%26quot%3BSave%20video%26quot%3B%20to%20download%20the%20video%20to%20your%20device.%20According%20to%20TikTok%2C%20if%20the%20%26quot%3BSave%20video%26quot%3B%20option%20does%20not%20appear%2C%20that%20means%20the%20person%20who%20posted%20the%20content%20does%20not%20allow%20video%20saves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20also%20allows%20you%20to%20save%20a%20copy%20of%20any%20content%20you%20post%20to%20your%20device%20while%20posting%20it%20to%20TikTok.%20Inside%20the%20%26quot%3Bpost%26quot%3B%20screen%2C%20you%20can%20tap%20the%20%26quot%3Bmore%20options%26quot%3B%20button%20and%20choose%20%26quot%3Bsave%20to%20device.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20also%20lets%20users%20download%20a%20copy%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.tiktok.com%2Fen%2Faccount-and-privacy%2Fpersonalized-ads-and-data%2Frequesting-your-data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20en