ition-7457952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stones%20Thrown%20At%20Train%20Headed%20To%20Prayagraj%20In%20UP%20For%20Maha%20Kumbh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20windowpane%20of%20a%20train%20headed%20from%20Surat%20to%20Prayagraj%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20damaged%20after%20a%20stone%20or%20stones%20struck%20its%20laminated%20glass%20surface%20while%20it%20was%20passing%20through%20Jalgaon%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20showed%20a%20video%2C%20sparking%20fear%20among%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20from%20the%20B6%20coach%20-%20which%20carried%2013%20people%20-%20women%2C%20children%20and%20devotees%20-%20of%20the%20Prayagraj%20Tapti%20Ganga%20Express.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20have%20left%20for%20Prayagraj%20from%20Surat%20Udhna.%20Today%20is%2012th%20January.%20All%20the%20passengers%20are%20with%20us.%20At%20least%203%20km%20ahead%20of%20Jalgaon%2C%20a%20stone%20was%20thrown%20by%20some%20anti-social%20elements.%20We%20request%20the%20Railway%20Minister%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajendfra%20Gupta%2C%20a%20passenger%20in%20the%20affected%20coach%2C%20showing%20the%20damaged%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20is%20steadily%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20train%20are%20going%20to%20Prayagraj%20for%20Maha%20Kumbh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railway%20and%20police%20have%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20stone%20was%20thrown%20on%20this%20train%2C%20coming%20from%20Surat%20Udhna%2C%20near%20Jalgaon.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20immediate%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20and%20four%20teams%20were%20deployed%20on%20the%20train.%20A%20complaint%20has%20also%20been%20lodged%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swapnil%20Neela%2C%20Ch