y%20veteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%201978.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20victory%20(of%20BJP)%20in%20Maharashtra%20ended%20the%20politics%20of%20instability%20and%20backstabbing%20started%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%201978.%20You%20(people)%20have%20buried%20such%20politics%2020-foot%20in%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20addressing%20a%20state%20BJP%20convention%20in%20Shirdi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201978%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20later%20founded%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Vasantdada%20Patil%20government%20with%2040%20MLAs%20and%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20nephew%2C%20split%20the%20party%20in%202023%20and%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%2C%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20was%20also%20a%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20emerged%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%202024%20state%20polls%2C%20winning%20132%20seats%2C%20which%20is%20also%20its%20highest%20seat%20tally%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%201978%20till%202024%2C%20Maharashtra%20was%20prone%20to%20political%20instability.%20You%20have%20shown%20the%20way%20by%20bringing%20in%20a%20stable%20and%20strong%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20stressed%20Mr%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Maharashtra%3A%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20The%20victory%20(of%20BJP)%20in%20Maharashtra%20ended%20the%20politics%20of%20instability%20and%20backstabbing%20started%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%201978.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20betrayed%20us%2C%20he%20left%20the%20ideology%20of%20Balasaheb%20in%202019.%20Today%20you%20have%20shown%20him%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h