m-businessmans-house-in-gurugram-police-7457145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Contender%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Leader%20Reacts%20To%20AAP's%20Chief%20Minister%20Face%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20on%20Sunday%20dismissed%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)'s%20claims%20that%20the%20opposition%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20consider%20projecting%20him%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20in%20next%20month's%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20saying%20he%20is%20not%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bidhuri%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20the%20polls%20from%20Kalkaji%20seat%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%2C%20made%20the%20clarification%20amid%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20National%20Convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20intends%20to%20field%20the%20former%20MP%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%20The%20opposition%20party%20has%2C%20however%2C%20repeatedly%20dismissed%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Bidhuri%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20as%20dedicated%20to%20the%20people%20as%20I%20am%20to%20my%20party.%20Talks%20about%20the%20chief%20minister's%20role%20for%20me%20are%20totally%20baseless.%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20timelessly%20as%20your%20servant.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20also%20said%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bloyal%20worker%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20has%20constantly%20blessed%20me%20and%20expressed%20trust%20in%20me.%20While%20I%20was%20holding%20important%20responsibilities%20for%20twenty-five%20years%2C%20the%20party%20made%20me%20an%20MP%20twice%20and%20an%20MLA%20thrice%20and%20has%20given%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20come%20to%20your%20door%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C