education%20scam%2C%20health%20scam%2C%20Sheeshmahal%20scam%2C%20broken%20roads%2C%20dirty%20drinking%20water%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20an%20alleged%20scam%20in%20the%20Delhi%20education%20department%2C%20the%20alleged%20Mohalla%20clinic%20scam%20and%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20bungalow%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20used%20as%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Atishi%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20reelection%20from%20Kalkaji%20seat%2C%20also%20claimed%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20going%20to%20name%20Mr%20Bidhuri%20as%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20and%20criticised%20the%20party%20for%20picking%20a%20leader%20who%20%26quot%3Bhurls%20the%20most%20abuses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20dismissed%20the%20claims%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20rumour%26quot%3B%20with%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20accusing%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20spreading%20canard%20for%20political%20mileage.%20%26quot%3BCan%20Kejriwal%20decide%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20ministerial%20face%3F%20Who%20is%20he%20to%20make%20such%20claims%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20addressing%20%26quot%3BJhuggi%20Basti%20Pradhan%20Sammelan%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Capital%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20attempting%20to%20manipulate%20public%20perception%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20understood%20his%20tactics.%20%26quot%3BLies%2C%20betrayal%20and%20going%20back%20on%20promises%26quot%3B%20are%20the%20qualities%20of%20Kejriwal%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bidhuri's%20recent%20remarks%20about%20Ms%20Atishi%20and%20Congress%20MP%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20had%20triggered%20a%20controversy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20had%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20against%20Ms%20Atishi's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20he%20said%20that%20would%20make%20roads%20in%20Kalkaji%2