C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20lies%20in%20an%20incident%20in%20his%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Eshikari%3C%2Fem%3E%20retires%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20on%2015%20August%2C%201917%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20was%20raised%20in%20the%20then%20princely%20state%20of%20Balrampur.%20Owing%20to%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20lineage%20%E2%80%94%20Jasbir%20Singh%20came%20from%20the%20royal%20family%20of%20Kapurthala%2C%20and%20served%20as%20a%20special%20manager%20for%20the%20nominal%20ruler%20of%20Balrampur%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20privy%20to%20the%20royal%20activities%2C%20which%20in%20those%20days%20included%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20niece%20Brinda%20Dubey%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20usually%20stayed%20there%20%5Bin%20Dudhwa%5D%20from%20Christmas%20until%20New%20Year.%20It%20was%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20jungle%20and%20almost%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334337%2Fbest-homestays-for-wildlife-safari-in-india-national-park-kanha-bandhavgarh-mudumalai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20with%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20he%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20grew%20close%20to%20the%20tigers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8uH-ZxyAWY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8uH-ZxyAWY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloadin