20for%20someone%20who%20has%20earned%20Rs%201%20to%20think%20about%20how%20to%20make%20it%20Rs%202%2C%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20double%20it.%20Everyone%20tries%20to%20do%20that.%20Many%20people%20work%20really%20hard%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20manages%20to%20break%20out%20of%20that%20cycle.%20I%20was%20lucky%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20knew%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20be%20a%20landowner%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarbeswar%20never%20gave%20up%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20improving%20his%20situation.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20adversity%2C%20he%20made%20a%20promise%3A%20%E2%80%9CThirty%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20made%20a%20promise%20to%20myself.%20I%20saw%20landowners%20being%20respected.%20We%20had%20nothing%20to%20our%20name%20%E2%80%94%20no%20land%2C%20no%20work%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20that%20respect.%20My%20only%20goal%20was%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20earn%20my%20family%20and%20me%20that%20honour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20would%20never%20be%20a%20landowner%2C%20nor%20would%20I%20become%20extremely%20wealthy%2C%20but%20I%20promised%20myself%20I%20would%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20earn%20that%20respect.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20shaped%20me%20into%20the%20person%20I%20am%20today%20%E2%80%94%20my%20character%2C%20my%20work%2C%20and%20my%20commitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20rising%20in-state%20tensions%2C%20the%20people%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%2C%20including%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20village%2C%20began%20claiming%20forest%20land%20as%